        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tighter mb-4">Why Your Shower Needs Regrouting</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary max-w-3xl mb-10">Grout is the first line of defence between your shower tiles and the wall behind them. When it cracks, crumbles, or goes mouldy, water penetrates the structure &mdash; causing hidden damage that gets worse every day you wait.</p>

